    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在虚拟现实死亡锦标赛中与杀手机器人展开剑斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受你的剑斩碎它们的金属身躯。借助我们惊人的体素战斗引擎，在你挥砍的精确位置造成伤害！！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/f08554f13db6147c60b664241d70b807.poster.avif?t=1760627715\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/f08554f13db6147c60b664241d70b807.webm?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/f08554f13db6147c60b664241d70b807.mp4?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是瞬移机器人Blink，最新的“循环跑者”角斗士，即将参加致命循环赛Crashloop，这是一场不死不休的Roguelike战斗运动。死亡后在无尽的循环中重生，跃过熔岩池，躲避炮塔火力，击败一波又一波的敌方防御机器人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/2bbb70d150c0c006d53a6cb13be5b930.poster.avif?t=1760627715\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/2bbb70d150c0c006d53a6cb13be5b930.webm?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/2bbb70d150c0c006d53a6cb13be5b930.mp4?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他循环跑者角逐，争取在Hyperdome中挑战队长，夺取他的权利！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/00db015ee483601df9df92612219a097.poster.avif?t=1760627715\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/00db015ee483601df9df92612219a097.webm?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/00db015ee483601df9df92612219a097.mp4?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挥舞各式各样的武器，找到你最喜欢的风格。激光武士刀、双手长矛、斧头和盾牌。如果你够胆量，就赤手空拳上阵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败其他循环跑者，夺取他们的涡轮拳套！喷射火焰、发射手里剑、减缓时间、召唤僵尸等等！用其他被击败的循环跑者的力量升级涡轮拳套，成为势不可挡的存在。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/7e1c28c9fa0bd81c8dd8603a2aee2af6.poster.avif?t=1760627715\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/7e1c28c9fa0bd81c8dd8603a2aee2af6.webm?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/7e1c28c9fa0bd81c8dd8603a2aee2af6.mp4?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗间隙，了解其他循环跑者，探索Crashloop的秘密。在他们的竞争中选择立场。用你的剑赢得他们的青睐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受体素破坏的力量。学会挥舞你的激光剑。你将获得自由，还是在Hyperdome的阴影中死去？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/7067c2d53052cd1bee008cc032163bd4.poster.avif?t=1760627715\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/7067c2d53052cd1bee008cc032163bd4.webm?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401230/extras/7067c2d53052cd1bee008cc032163bd4.mp4?t=1760627715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
